short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replace new tab screen with personal dashboard.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Your will get on every new tab a random unsplash background and Google Tasks on it, to make You more productive!

【Coming soon】
Clockify integrations (add task, worklog, etc)

【Features】
Background from unsplash
Tasklist with using Google Tasks API (Using OAuth 2.0)
Focus Stopper (save data to local storage)
Add shortcuts (Q - hide/show todolist, W,E - change todolist)

【Update】
2020.02.15. Fix key bindings
2020.02.02. Add Q, W, E hotkeys
2019.12.24. Upload the first version
